      <li><strong>ChatGPT</strong>: Copywriting and creative ideation</li>
      <li><strong>Jasper</strong>: Template-based marketing copy production</li>
      <li><strong>Copy.ai</strong>: Social media content generation</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>2. Visual Design Tools</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Midjourney</strong>: Creative poster design</li>
      <li><strong>DALL-E</strong>: Product image generation</li>
